default6. ConclusiondefaultWe thank the House of Commons for this op
defaultportunity to present evidence regarding the unique circumstances of the Israeli Palestinian conflict, and for the need for increased civil society actions that will build trust among individuals on both sides. Popular support for a formal peace agreement w
defaultill give leaders the power to make what seems now to be a distant, unlikely possibility into a viable endeavor.
